title: #56: The Victims of the Baton Rouge Killings
description:
The Real Crime Profile team (Jim Clemente, Laura Richards and Lisa Zambetti) honors the victims and examine the cases regarding a killing spree that terrorized Baton Rouge, Louisiana between 1992 and 2003.
